      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «إِذَا صَحَّ هِلاَلُ رَجَبٍ فَعُدَّ تِسْعَةً وَ خَمْسِينَ يَوْماً وَ صُمْ يَوْمَ اَلسِّتِّينَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1918 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"If the crescent of Rajab is confirmed, count fifty-nine days and fast on the sixtieth day.\""
        ]
      }
